CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, September 22, 1962, pg. 8, reads: "The Goodes - Lieut. and Mrs. Malvin Russell Goode (center) are pictured with Mr. and Mrs. Malvin R. Goode, parents of the groom, following their wedding last Saturday. The groom met his bride, the former Antje (Angie) Pilz, when he was stationed with the U.S. Air Force in Germany. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Groom Malvin Russell Goode Jr., wearing United States Air Force dress uniform, and bride Antije (Angie) Pilz wearing short sleeved knee length dress, standing with Dorothy Grier and Robert Grier, in home of Mr. and Mrs. Mal Goode Sr.
